Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:04.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shortly after a month had passed since entering school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:09.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...much like Sisyphus forced to eternally roll a boulder uphill...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:14.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'd had my fill of this mandatory morning hiking course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:16.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then, as if being dealt the final blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:22.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...my normal life came to a grinding halt when the incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:23.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Began would be more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:30.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If there isn't one, I just have to make it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:31.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A club!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:33.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:36.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came up with a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,SOS Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to Haruhi Suzumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:45.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...eccentric among eccentrics, my journey through never-ending hell had begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:49.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:52.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that I had to do today's class duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry to the staff office and ask for the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:55.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:00.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's hard to believe a girl like her is in the same class when...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:07.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What else do you think we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:08.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:12.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to get my hands on a mysterious transfer student, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:13.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Establish the context before you start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:18.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What the SOS Brigade needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:20.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I at least want a mysterious transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to define mysterious first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:27.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't even been two months since the new term began.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:31.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who transfers in at this point must qualify as mysterious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:32.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You agree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:35.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the student's dad was suddenly transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:36.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:40.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you consider normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:40.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if a mysterious transfer student will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you don't give a damn what I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:51.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:28.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would appear that a rumor had spread that Haruhi and I were plotting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:27.55,HaruhiTitleOverlay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(470,500)\fs28\pos(99,45)}The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya II
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you and Suzumiya up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:40.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who would like to know exactly what the hell we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not in middle school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you render the grounds unusable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll at least suspend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:54.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to at least prevent Yuki Nagato and Mikuru Asahina-san from coming to any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:55.69,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(348,427,348,416)\fs24\1c&HFFFFFF&}CHIEF
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After the SOS Brigade was founded...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.95,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(348,400,348,386)\fs22\1c&HFFFFFF&}CHIEF
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:00.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the bleakness of the former literary clubroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was replaced by a growing number of items.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean. Is she planning on living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:09.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A computer would be nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:14.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're living in the information age and yet we don't have a single computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can't forgive who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go scrounge one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually have any leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on raiding an electronics store?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.27,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H77\fs24\frz1.4\frx3\fry-3\fscy120\bord0.5\1a&H33&\3c&H000000&\pos(487,273)}Computer Research Society
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one much closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:35.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to take one set of computer and peripherals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:38.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:44.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one reason I would come in person to the Computer Research Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I only need one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so give me a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One can't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:53.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The SOS Brigade Chief, Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These two are subordinates #1 and #2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your grumbling and hand one over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For what reason!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I would ever do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have my own ideas about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you trying to do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:31.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One more shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk. Tsk. Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:44.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got pictures of your sexual harassment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want me to spread these pictures around school...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...pay up and hand over a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:52.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You forced me to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:57.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And how many people do you think will believe your words?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All the members here are witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the prez's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:11.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say that the whole club was planning on ****-****** her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's taking it too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:14.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:15.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to hand it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:16.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Su-Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take whichever one you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}It wasn't your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this supposed to be a comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}But!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one's the newest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:48.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to tell you that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:59.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked over all the newest models at the computer shop yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:08.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We just bought that last month!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it, you thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:29.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...after blackmailing herself a spanking new computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Haruhi, discovering that the literary clubroom wasn't equipped for Internet use...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...summoned the Computer Society's president and members...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and had them run a LAN cable between our rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:40.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She even had him set it up so we could connect through the school's domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is what you call an extortionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:58.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get involved with such a weird group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what else she'll do to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:04.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:05.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:21.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This was probably an inevitability on this time plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:27.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm concerned about why Nagato-san is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be inexperienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I hope to get along with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:41.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...please call me Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:46.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well...
