Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Who's going to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That site or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:55.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got time, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find more members.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have it finished in a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:07.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't participate in any activities until a site's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a website, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And despite all the grumbling, I actually enjoyed making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:23.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Computer Society had installed most of the necessary programs so it was pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:25.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not a bad way to kill time during lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.17,HaruhiWebsite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H33\fs9\pos(267,89)}You are the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.17,HaruhiWebsite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H33\fs9\pos(344,89)}th visitor to this site.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.17,HaruhiWebsite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.8\pos(322,218)\c&H151CDF&}Welcome to the SOS Brigade's Website!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.17,HaruhiWebsite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\fs26\c&HCC2A2A&\pos(317,298)}Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.17,HaruhiWebsite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\fs12\pos(330,364)}Mail us at
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.17,HaruhiWebsite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H33\fs9\pos(318,397)}This website is best viewed at 1024x768.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Speaking of which, what am I supposed to put on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:34.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, I still have no idea what the SOS Brigade does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything you want to put on the site?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:44.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not that I care, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she does go to class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:08.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.13,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\alpha&H22&\frx25\frz53\fs14\bord0\fscy108\shad0\pos(218,209)}Dan Simmons
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still have my misgivings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so why is it that I continue commuting to the clubroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this the power of habit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:44.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yeah. Are these two really that bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though I guess I'm not one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:48.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Suzumiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:49.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was already gone during sixth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she's off extorting more equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be forced to do something like yesterday again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'll do everything I can to prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yahoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First up is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:25.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A proclamation of the SOS Brigade creed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ta-ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:34.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to distribute flyers wearing these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be plenty of students heading home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:39.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan's the one who's wearing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:44.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:45.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bunny girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:49.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:50.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get changed! Get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off! Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suzumiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:11:59.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:03.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it all off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me undress myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:21.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's like some evil feudal lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:28.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be perfect for attracting attention, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,More like suck in attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I could only buy two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the full set so it was expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do they sell this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered it online.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:52.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:56.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be honest, I can't get enough of that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My passion is running wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:10.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still feel their body heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:23.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:31.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A proclamation of the SOS Brigade creed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:35.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our SOS Brigade is looking for mysteries of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People who have experienced something mysterious in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:43.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People who have run into something mysterious recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:46.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People who plan on a mysterious experience in the near future...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If any of the above apply to you, come see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will solve your problem on the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, a normal mystery will not do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:58.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be a mystery that wows us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make note of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:03.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I'm starting to understand the purpose of this brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those stupid teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're such a pain! A pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there some kind of a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Way beyond that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We hadn't even distributed half the flyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the teachers told us to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do they think they are!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If two bunny girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:26.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...start handing out flyers at the front gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...people who aren't teachers will come running.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan started sobbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dragged to the student guidance office...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even that handball moron Okabe was brought in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were probably all on the verge of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:39.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:42.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to keep crying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:47.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:58.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:02.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I become ruined for marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...will you take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From behind, you look like a student who just failed to get into college.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or a salaryman after buying a house beyond his budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:21.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're going to call me that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:29.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day, the name Haruhi Suzumiya had transcended mere notoriety...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and became common knowledge for all students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:40.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally become one of Suzumiya's merry friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:40.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's even worse is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Asahina-san's name and mine had become associated with hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:49.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there were bunny girls standing at the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one was that second-year, Asahina-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:59.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole school has their attention on you guys now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this SOS Brigade?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you people are having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think that was going a bit too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:18.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asahina-san was absent from school that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we ever get e-mails?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that publicity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There aren't any people curious enough to want to get involved after witnessing your publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll admit that you've made us famous though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mikuru-chan absent today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She might not ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:38.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope she doesn't become traumatized by the ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I even brought a new outfit for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'm going to wear it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:47.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's no fun when Mikuru-chan isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You could have Nagato wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'd probably put it on without any complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I get the feeling I wouldn't mind seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:00.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The SOS Brigade was just formed and we're already sitting around doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're all holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to keep the mystery to themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:06.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you ask anybody here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:10.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...they'll say, "No, there aren't any."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:16.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way this little public high school would have mysteries bouncing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is that you understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just that you have nowhere to vent the frustrations of youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and that restlessness is leading you down a different path.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:29.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Snap out of it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How about you go find some handsome guy and walk home from school together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or go see a movie on Sundays?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:38.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And join some sports club and knock yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'd make you a regular member in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:42.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:52.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:57.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Read what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:00.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I return it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:07.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:10.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's never one to mince words, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Read it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:18.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
