Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Kyon-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk while eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was today okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you possibly waiting here yesterday as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:32.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:38.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:42.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only one who is ever here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're living alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:44.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:53.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:36.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me why you brought me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you couldn't tell me at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:50.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I need to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:04.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Suzumiya and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:10.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is difficult to convey in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:14.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Discrepancies may arise during the transmission of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:17.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:23.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi Suzumiya and I are not ordinary humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of knew that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:28.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:35.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not referring to the absence of universally accepted personality traits...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:43.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She and I are different from the vast majority of humans like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:49.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An organic life contact-purpose humanoid interface...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:54.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...created by the Data Integration Thought Entity which supervises this galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:56.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:21:59.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:03.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In more common terminology...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:05.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I would be classified as an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alien?
